data.description: Great opportunity in Grove Park area, can be great Residential Income, large backyard with numerous potential, 5 bedrooms 4 bathrooms, master on main, open floor plan, 2 bedrooms upstairs with its own private bathroom, 2 other bedrooms share a bathroom, walk-in closets, new quartz countertop in kitchen and stainless steel appliances, backsplash, new up-to-date light fixtures and hardware through-out the home, new basins in all bathrooms and faucets, washer and dryer included, new wood blinds on main, home has great possibilities (rental), close to Anderson Park and Westside Park, minutes to beltline, Mercedes Benz Stadium and Aquarium, downtown, hospitals, airport, 75/85, and easy access to I-20 & 285.
